---
title: "Introduction to research methodology"
---

This section will provide an overview of the methodology used by the Syrian Archive in carrying out this research. The methodology section will be broken into the following sub-sections:

A) [Collection and archival methodology](en/topics/1-collection-archival/1-intro)
B) [Initial verification methodology](en/topics/2-basic-verification/1-intro)
C) [In-depth verification methodology](en/topics/3-in-depth-investigations/1-intro).
